# VirtualBox Networking Configuration

## Objective
Configure an isolated internal network for SOC lab communication.

## Steps
1. Power off all virtual machines
2. Open VM Settings â†’ Network
3. Set Adapter 1 to NAT Network
4. Name the network `SOC-LAB`
5. Repeat for all lab VMs

## Validation
- Verified IP connectivity between Kali Linux and Windows Server
